{{version024}}
{{flavour|Releases a thick cloud of ink to obscure vision.}}

'''Ink Cloud''' is a monsters-only escape spell which functions similarly to a [[scroll of fog]], filling the [[water]] with short-lived [[cloud]]s of ink to block your [[line of sight]] while the caster makes its escape. Unlike other types of clouds, ink clouds can only spread through water.

